    dc:description "Figure 8. Deltamysis lowryi sp. nov., holotype, male, 4 mm, New South Wales,Yamba,AM P.98699:(A) maxilla 2, posterior; (B) maxilliped 2 endopod, anterior; (C) pereopod 1 endopod, posterior; (D) pereopod 1 distal part, posterior; (E) pereopod 4 endopod, anterior; (F) pereopod 6, posterior; (G) pereopod 1 distal part, posterior. Scales (mm): A, D, G = 0.25; B, C, E, F = 0.5." ;
